name: I Love Kabuki-cho
description: This is a cinemagraph I created of a photo I took at Kabuki-cho, Tokyo. It is representation of the great scenery that Tokyo had to offer me while I was there. In Kabukicho so many people come to walk around, go on dates, eat dinner, or just have fun in other ways. It is the red light district after all. Twitter: @lllonilll
